程序包 com.module.interaction

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    DataPackageParser
    You can receive the raw data returned by module.In order to get the data information you must resolve it according to the protocol of module.Then you can invoke method #analyData(byte[]) in #DataPackageProcess put the data package to it.The default implementation of {
    ModuleConnector
    The interface manage the connector of module.
    RXTXListener
    Implement this interface who want to listen sending data to reader,receiving data from reader,and the connection missing with reader.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    DataPackageProcess
    The return data process class.This class resolve the return data package to find the information you want to get.The method DataPackageProcess.analyData(byte[]) receive the complete data package returned by module.
    ReaderHelper
    Base class to operate all the modules.This class include the read and write functions to module.
